## what i learned:

### false positive
- when an alert appears suspicious but turns out to be a legitimate activity

### Suspicious Sequences

A sequence of events can be more important than individual events.

Example:
Successful Login
→ Password Changed
→ MFA Disabled
→ Login From New Country
→ Large File Download

This may indicate potential compromise and should be investigated.

